<br>
1) Try to explain the glories of Do-It-Yourself<br>
<br>
2) When this doesn't work (it almost never does, but I keep hoping)...<br>
/roar<br>
/duel<br>
<br>
Yes, I know they are in no real danger from me unless they care to accept, but it seems to get the point across rather better than number 1.<br>
<br>
